I told him I was under the legal drinking age but he told me that he wouldn’t tell anyone. I drank it mostly because of how chill this app was. But a couple weeks later I started coughing up a storm so I got tested for COVID. But the test took out a chunk of my brain on accident and now I can’t remember where I live. On top of that the test came back positive. So now I have COVID-19 and I haven’t seen my since because I lost part of my brain. This app sucks😡😡😡😡😡 

Edit: It also gave me HIV
